AB  - In order to better release the production efficiency of automatic terminal, improve the comprehensive benefits, stimulate the endogenous power of smart port logistics, the new dimension of supporting service of automatic terminal is explored, and the evaluation index system and model of innovative service level of fuzzy automatic terminal are established. The automatic terminals of seven ports were selected as samples, collected data, and combined with quantitative and qualitative methods to demonstrate and correct the mechanism and function of the evaluation model. The conclusion shows that the innovative service of integrated logistics is accurate, effective and scientific. Its method is convenient, easy to operate and reasonable demonstration, which provides important reference for the optimization of operation mode and the improvement of management ability.
